{
  "id": "6a3d18b872bd1ecf857426ac",
  "title": "中の下",
  "created": 1782388923,
  "updated": 1782389386,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a3d18b872bd1ecf857426ac",
      "text": "中の下",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1782388923,
      "updated": 1782388923
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3d193200000000004af1d8",
      "text": "下と言うほど下ではないが中と言うのもなんだかなぁというお気持ちの現れ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1782389043,
      "updated": 1782389043
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3d18bd00000000004af1d6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1782388926,
      "updated": 1782388926
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3d193400000000004af1d9",
      "text": "3段階評価上中下の中を更に3段階に分けた下",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1782389044,
      "updated": 1782389044
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3d198600000000004af1e4",
      "text": " 全部並べて個人的な印象を添えてみよう[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1782389127,
      "updated": 1782389304
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3d193700000000004af1da",
      "text": " \t上の上：もっと綺羅びやかな表現が使われる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1782389047,
      "updated": 1782389190
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3d194000000000004af1dc",
      "text": " \t上の中：",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1782389056,
      "updated": 1782389152
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3d194300000000004af1dd",
      "text": " \t上の下：上げて落とすみたいな感じで聞く",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1782389060,
      "updated": 1782389244
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3d194600000000004af1de",
      "text": " \t中の上：たまに聞く",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1782389062,
      "updated": 1782389198
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3d194a00000000004af1df",
      "text": " \t中の中：",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1782389067,
      "updated": 1782389147
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3d194f00000000004af1e0",
      "text": " \t中の下：よく聞く",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1782389071,
      "updated": 1782389144
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3d195100000000004af1e1",
      "text": " \t下の上：",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1782389074,
      "updated": 1782389145
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3d195500000000004af1e2",
      "text": " \t下の中：",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1782389077,
      "updated": 1782389146
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3d195800000000004af1e3",
      "text": " \t下の下：自分に対して物凄い卑下しているか、相手に対して物凄い貶しているニュアンスでに聞くことがある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1782389080,
      "updated": 1782389386
    },
